<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ910213-0137</DOCNO><DOCID>910213-0137.</DOCID><HL>   Who's News:   Sterling Optical Corp.</HL><DATE>02/13/91</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION</SO><CO>   WNEWS EYE</CO><IN>SPECIALTY RETAILERS (OTS)</IN><LP>   STERLING OPTICAL Corp. (Hackensack, N.J.) -- GeorgeCasabona was named executive vice president at this opticalretailing company. Mr. Casabona, previously a vice president,will continue as chief financial officer and a director. Inaddition, Charles E. Gross, executive vice president ofretail operations, was named a director, increasing boardmembership to 12.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>